Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王 王...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Comment: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.37,OP,,0,0,0,,/----OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:04.46,OP,,0,0,0,,例えば目が覚めて「すべては幻だ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.63,OP,,0,0,0,,奇跡めいた妄想を叶えて欲しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.34,OP,,0,0,0,,僕が描いた罪で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.02,OP,,0,0,0,,結末を満たさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:37.86,OP,,0,0,0,,壊し続けた僕は何かを救えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:43.95,OP,,0,0,0,,変わり果てた今に革命のナイフ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}ほどけるように刺して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:52.00,OP,,0,0,0,,光に満ちたさよならを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.59,OP,,0,0,0,,I will miss you, I will miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}罰を僕に与えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:05.68,OP,,0,0,0,,君はまだ僕を愛してはくれるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:11.90,OP,,0,0,0,,「僕じゃなきゃ」「僕じゃダメだ」「僕じゃなきゃ」がループする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:18.24,OP,,0,0,0,,僕を刺したナイフさえも  いつかきっと光を射すから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:04.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,希望某天醒来 发现一切都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我多想这种奇迹般的妄想能成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不要让我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,成为故事的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:37.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,破坏众多存在的我 又拯救了什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:43.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,给面目全非的如今 一场革命的刀光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}仿佛要彻底获得解脱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:52.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,渴求那个充满光明的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:58.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur5\3c&H1E1E1E&\3a&H4C&}给我应有的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:05.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,你仍旧愿意爱我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:11.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,陷入「非我不可」「我不行的」「非我不可」的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:18.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,刺向我的刀光 迟早也会毁灭那片光明
Comment: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,/----08----
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑磐特等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么想和我一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我听说是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那儿子总是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓜江是好友 也是竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我看着你就会想起干人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦 今天还是个重要的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你拒绝审问一事将会被记录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你想特意证明一下是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的精神有多么清廉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有问题想问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证明一件事需要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是证人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香 带大家去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我逃啊 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 四方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带那些孩子们快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要给我死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用昆克能斩断吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有技巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在CCG战斗真是愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小死堪 我来助阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和茨桥一等那时相同的做法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和报告书上写得一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雄雌雄雌...死...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然和喰种联手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你可没法辩解了吧 旧多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小少爷 你认为喰种和人类共同的敌人是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界就是个马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都很有趣但无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:11.49,Comments,,0,0,0,,胡乱之母\NSSS等级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士皇和理界负责左边 夕作负责右边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是敌人 也让我很钦佩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑磐...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么 不过是个重伤的老不死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他了啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很突然 不过鸡和鸡蛋的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在刚才得出了一定是先有鸡这个结论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等盖饭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和利世小姐...不对 是和我一样的赫子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种恢复能力 难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事啊 能让开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绯世 丑话说在前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:41.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs125\pos(460,992)}觉醒之{\c&H1100DF&}子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂啊 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么有马先生把这种事托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托付给我是因为他信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信无论处于什么状况 我都会为了有马先生而战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有马先生之所以没有托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因为相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论处于什么状况 都会为了正义而战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的这些我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不给我最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是王的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡乱的躯体被...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不行 没有不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秃子?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能保护好干人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我当时能更强...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉 都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我所憎恨的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是当时什么都做不到的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个幼小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我狭小的内心实在无法全部承受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不把责任推给其他人 我实在受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的和干人先生非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一击真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直吵死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸手特等?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是副什么样子 阿磐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丸...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会陪你一起的 今后也永远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丸手特等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请解释一下是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:02.41,Comments,,0,0,0,,注: 我是永近英良 帮帮我们 瓜江
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,董香...
